title: I Was Scammed by the Promise of Passive Real Estate Income (Hour 1)
description:
Rachel Cruze & George Kamel discuss:

Getting family on board with the Ramsey plan,

Getting out of the rental game,

Why passive income from real estate is a myth.

Moving out of your parents' house,

Getting started on Baby Step 1,

Leaving a stable job to find better pay.
